#H bit | smtpStat | Description
#H =============================================================================
     0 | 0x01     | SMTP ports found
     1 | 0x02     | Authentication pending
     2 | 0x04     | Data download pending
     3 | 0x08     | User password pending

     4 | 0x10     | Flow write finished
     5 | 0x20     | -
#E   6 | 0x40     | File error
#W   7 | 0x80     | Array overflow... increase one of SMTP_MAX[CUPSRT]NM
